<div class="title">Perfect Combination</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamine (Adderall), Promethazine (Phenergan) & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Greenman&Exact=1">Greenman</a></div>


